  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 216.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "For instance, in Nahariyyah, or the Nahariyyah Haganah command of the Western Galilee, would be notified, well, we are expecting a ship, for instance, the with, I don't know, 1,600 people, some-- something like that, and they are due on this date.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they-- we never knew when, because they used to try to outmaneuver the British Navy, the British Air Force, and they would go from place to place to place, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But the moment the ship would arrive by the-- by the shores, then there were a multitude of young men, Haganah young men, we used to swim with ropes to-- close to the sea and have these heavy ropes.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then what happens in [? there, ?] and it's hard to understand, is the fact that many people that couldn't even swim, the moment they saw the shores they would jump out of the boat.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And many times you couldn't even stand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The-- the water was above your head.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And therefore, the Haganah, the young men, were there to help these people and guide them through the ropes into the shores.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Into the shores, put it in a bus, in a car, et cetera, and haul them away to freedom.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Undescribable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You cannot describe that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the-- just to be free in the land of Israel, it was the ultimate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it's hard to describe the-- the-- the tears that-- that-- that you would see in their faces, the happy-- tears of happiness in this case.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
